The '''Buick GL6''' is a 6-seater [[compact MPV]] produced by [[Buick]] exclusively for the Chinese market. The GL6 is positioned below the successful [[Buick GL8|GL8]] to aim for the lower-priced MPV market. Pricing starts around $25,000 (estimate in U.S. dollars, converted from Chinese yuan).<ref>{{cite web|url=https://carnewschina.com/2017/09/04/spy-shots-buick-gl6-mpv-photo-shooted-china/|title=Spy Shots: Buick GL6 MPV Is Photo-Shooted &#91;sic&#93; in China}}</ref>

